## Description {#details}

Represent a node in the directed graph.

The node has a (possibly empty) list of outgoing edges.

Definition at line 73 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/adt/directedgraph-h">DirectedGraph.h</a>.
